stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> ScheduledBackup : Start Backup
    ScheduledBackup --> InProgress : Backup in Progress
    InProgress --> Completed : Backup Successful
    InProgress --> Failed : Backup Failed
    Completed --> Idle : Next Scheduled Backup
    Failed --> Retry : Retry Backup
    Retry --> InProgress : Backup in Progress
    Retry --> Idle : Abort Backup